-- Austria, banks to start Hypo Alpe Adria bad bank talks
-- By Michael Shields in Vienna
-- Mon Jan 27, 2014 04:29AM EST
-- None



VIENNA, Jan 27 (Reuters) - The Austrian government has decided to launch talks with commercial banks about winning their support to find a solution for troubled nationalized lender Hypo Alpe Adria [HAABI.UL], finance minister Michael Spindelegger told reporters on Monday.

